members.member:

      Creates a link to custom actions in PDF document.

The rectangle for active click.
The number of original page where rectangle bound with link will be created.
The colour of rectangle for active click.
The array of actions (members of PredefinedAction enum) corresponding to executing menu items in Acrobat viewer./// 

      PdfContentEditor editor = new PdfContentEditor();
      editor.BindPdf("example.pdf");
      editor.CreateCustomActionLink(new System.Drawing.Rectangle(0, 0, 100, 100),
          1, System.Drawing.Color.Red,
          new Enum[] { PredefinedAction.FirstPage, PredefinedAction.PrintDialog });
      editor.Save("example_out.pdf");


      Creates a link to launch an application in PDF document.

The rectangle for active click.
The path of application to be launched.
The number of original page where rectangle bound with link will be created.
The colour of rectangle for active click.
The array of actions (members of PredefinedAction enum) corresponding to executing menu items in Acrobat viewer./// 

      PdfContentEditor editor = new PdfContentEditor();
      editor.BindPdf("example.pdf");
      editor.CreateApplicationLink(new System.Drawing.Rectangle(0, 0, 100, 100),
          "explorer", 1, System.Drawing.Color.Red,
          new Enum[] { PredefinedAction.FirstPage, PredefinedAction.PrintDialog });
      editor.Save("example_out.pdf");

